data.description: Come see this Cobb beauty! Sitting on ALMOST AN ACRE of land this home is perfect for any buyer. Garrett Springs is a quiet, well maintained community with NO HOA! This home is freshly painted, boasts a sizable back deck, enclosed porch with a fenced back yard. The master is large and sure to fit all your furnishings. The finished basement can be used as a man cave, media room, home gym or office space. There is also a full bathroom in the basement. Please schedule through ShowingTime. The seller works from home and welcomes weekday showings while he is in the basement working. The seller will also need 30 days temporary occupancy. When submitting offers please provide proof of funds and preapproval letters. Please no blind offers or esign invites. We thank you for your interest in the property and as always, Thank you for showing!
